{"tid":338210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女櫃員巴士上推跌阿婆打車長判服務令 官指被告已知錯勿公審","createTime":"2017-07-28T04:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T08:48:54.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52be5cb1057b2f00d535605959b22b08f2626eb1","tid":338210,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170728/large/1501214281_aa08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170728%2Flarge%2F1501214281_aa08.jpg&h=326ae9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年輕銀行女櫃員於巴士上被六旬婦要求移開霸佔座位的背包，兩人因而爭執，女櫃員及後推跌對方，並襲擊上前追截的女車長。女櫃員早前在裁判法院承認普通襲擊及襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，裁判官今判被告接受100小時社會服務令及向兩名傷者各賠償5,000元。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又指，案發時被告陳靄婷(28歲)外祖父病危，信納被告因家事感覺焦慮而犯案，而被告外祖父於案發兩日後死亡。裁判官更提高聲線稱：「各界不要再公審一個有悔意同知錯嘅年輕人」。<br />\n<br />\n律師今求情指，被告為人孝順，是一名乖孩子，犯案與其性格不符，被告事後已深切懊悔，希望給予機會年青人。<br />\n<br />\n案發於本年5月7日，被告乘搭215X號巴士時，被一名六旬婦要求移開霸佔座位的背包以讓她坐下，二人因此爭執。其後被告於啟田邨打算離座下車時，疑嫌六旬婦動作緩慢而伸手將她推倒地上。女車長見狀下車追截，遭被告推跌及狂踢。最終被告因在街上失足仆倒而束手就擒。"},{"pid":"60fbb16458155efb5330e7aba7c16546451b1bd9","tid":338210,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefb0e6b1f4c90dbbd1288528199eb4779c1bf2f","tid":338210,"uid":61359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"係咪仆街廢老阻人落車果單？"},{"pid":"34e37608f2da8b6c9c0d6d4bd287ebe3a68930de","tid":338210,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"87ebee04bc9110f3cfea596ed5c14e602b30703a","tid":338210,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"叫d廢老唔好係fb公審人先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc00bfa48e19f581ca95fd1338303f6e23cd4176","tid":338210,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"點會公審 讚好都來唔切"},{"pid":"deb71ecf137fb431ec40e4d9f115f990668e2572","tid":338210,"uid":38206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪仆街廢老阻人落車果單？</blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"77b7d834b4f7a0c1dc12176284cd0a0efec89ec0","tid":338210,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"D死肥西係霸道D"},{"pid":"1f2f8545527dab113ed1e143831b368a8b5942da","tid":338210,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:15:09.000Z","msg":"打柒啲廢老就岩"},{"pid":"67563d0c3f6523e410b20dbfaf61189ee047e8a1","tid":338210,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"D廢老成日霸位搞到人無得坐"},{"pid":"a433427dd6b6fb8adeeb6a05e06fd076dc4ed01f","tid":338210,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D廢老成日霸位搞到人無得坐</blockquote><br />\n睇錯，原來係肥西霸位"},{"pid":"0205f172067b79ff212e45e0619897a3202c2813","tid":338210,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"公審個廢老呀婆就真啦<br />\n佢仆撚死咗未呀?未死好快撚啲跳樓啦死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664be1c1dc78a84448cc822f6d88b3ba78850550","tid":338210,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾官<br />\n賣下小強又無事<br />\n難怪香港愈來愈多偽君子"},{"pid":"13e3e84eb524ad853742d17d572f177cd1e9d6bd","tid":338210,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"公審廢老就差唔多<br />\n呢個女中豪傑嚟㗎"}]}